Custom Elements Sample

Description :
This is a plug-in for DAZ Studio that shows the basics of file IO using DSON on custom implementations of a scene data item.
 
Concepts Covered :
  • DSON File IO
  • Custom Scene Data
  • Model View Controller Paradigm
  • UI
